    "text": "$$\n\\overrightarrow{AD} = \\overrightarrow{BC} \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} a - 5 = 4 \\\\ b - 3 = -6 \\\\ c - 1 = 2 \\end{cases} \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} a = 9 \\\\ b = -3 \\\\ c = 3 \\end{cases} .\n$$"
